elements.name: Create Product Based New requirement Acq

steps.name: User on program manager dashboard
User clicks on create new
User selects create new requirement and clicks next
User selects Products or Services and clicks next
User selects category of contracting and clicks next
User selects products and service PSC Considerations and clicks next
User types keywords or phrases and clicks next
User selects anticipated award date and clicks next
User selects no for unusual and compelling urgency and clicks next
User enters estimated budget and clicks next
User enters project title and clicks submit

User should see options like “General”, “Statement of Work”, “Market Research”, “Funding”, “Evaluations”, “Security”, “Other Considerations”, “Attachments”, “Points of Contact”, “Resources” on the left nav

User clicks on the “Other Considerations” option on the left nav

elements.name: After Creating acquisition user navigates to point of contact page and shares with the Contracting Officer

steps.name: User is on project general page
User clicks on point of contact in the left side navigation
User sees the point of contact page
User should be able to select one of the contracting officers from the drop-down
User should see information populated in “Contact Information”, “Email” and “Phone Number” fields upon selecting contracting officers’ name in “Contracting officer” field
Acquistion will be shared with selected CO

elements.name: Deletion of “Contracting Officer” information from the “Points of Contact” page

steps.name: User is on POC page
User clicks on the “Trash” symbol beside the “Contracting officer” field
User should see all the pre-filled information deleted from the fields
User adds POC

description: Contracting Officer Logs in to the account and checks the acquistion that was shared and fills the required information and then accepts and draft the solicitation
name: Drafting Solicitation

elements.name: Contracting officer logs in to the account and checks the acquisition

User enters CO credentials and logs in
User sees the CO dashboard

elements.name: Contracting officer reviews the shared acquisition

steps.name: User is on dashboard
User sees the shared acquisition and clicks on review button
User sees the general page of the acquisition

elements.name: “Draft Solicitation” in Acquisition page for the “Streamlined” version of acquisition

steps.name: User is on general page
User selects Streamlined from the below radio buttons in Commercial Purchase section in the General page of acquisition
User clicks on the “Draft Solicitation” button on the top right in the Acquisition page which he is reviewing after the acquisition is successfully accepted
User should see a notification saying on the top right saying “Initiated successfully” “AI has built the form successfully” on the next window
User should see a “Streamlined” version of acquisition in the next window
